{"tid":493484,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Razer Phone 雷蛇手機香港發佈上市，價格合理？","createTime":"2017-12-08T14:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T06:56:02.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1aec348071e7681114fe2398584d40039436b3a0","tid":493484,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:29:36.000Z","msg":"Razer 最近香港 IPO，正式上市之後股價似乎已經穿了 IPO，買了股票的只可苦笑。在雷蛇宣佈 IPO 當日亦同時發佈了他們的第一部針對電競而推出的手機 Razer Phone 雷蛇手機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xb4KkkAq376GzKus8Fz0oA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/bf4bae26db422e6f0bae0770e100340f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fxb4KkkAq376GzKus8Fz0oA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Filoveapps.com%2Fbf4bae26db422e6f0bae0770e100340f&h=c0bcbc04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雷蛇手機在海外已經開賣，海外定價就要700美元。而今日 Razer 正式在香港發佈，究竟香港定價方面又是如何？<br />\n<br />\nRazer Phone 針對手機電競遊戲設計所以在規格上亦作出調整，比如 Snapdragon 835 處理器 和 8GB RAM 都是現時最頂級的手機規格，然後是電池方面亦配上 4000mAh 超大電量以有足夠電力對遊戲續航。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OmIdY.5F5aeZrmM9FqqtVQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/5f59fb4929040a00ec713e81766d0e4a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOmIdY.5F5aeZrmM9FqqtVQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Filoveapps.com%2F5f59fb4929040a00ec713e81766d0e4a&h=19bed8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最強的應該是屏幕，配備的是 5.7吋 IGZO LCD，2K 的解析度，而且是全球第一部手機屏幕達到 120Hz，比起一般旗艦手機只 60Hz，這真的強太多了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mCnSQLWFIZUPyrsVA4SjgQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/a0497d0be8ff0dbb03d915b951ecc45c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmCnSQLWFIZUPyrsVA4SjgQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Filoveapps.com%2Fa0497d0be8ff0dbb03d915b951ecc45c&h=8c6d7fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n音效亦是打機最基本需求之一，所以 Razer Phone 配備杜比 ATMOS 驅動前置雙喇叭，而主機身沒有 3.5mm 插口，但就支援 THX 認證的 USB-C 24bit DAC。<br />\n<br />\n最終還是看定價，香港 Razer Phone 雷蛇手機定價為 HK$5999 ，純規格而言還是有一定吸引力。12月9日起在 RazerStore HK 及其官網開賣，12月16日起於 hmv 銅鑼灣及 3Shop 有售。<br />\n<br />\n電訊商方面，Razer Phone 於 3HK 有售，現時已有零機價 Plan，詳情可看下表：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/o.OdT9HeN8Cc1tVEX2Vm9g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/iloveapps.com/890fe314a9a4f37713c2b1ec3e9061cd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fo.OdT9HeN8Cc1tVEX2Vm9g--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Filoveapps.com%2F890fe314a9a4f37713c2b1ec3e9061cd&h=a2bc7a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nRazer Phone &ndash; 詳細規格<br />\n<br />\n處理器\tQualcomm&reg; Snapdragon&trade; 835<br />\n系統記憶體\t8GB 雙頻 (LPDDR4, 1866MHz)<br />\n儲存空間\t內置: 64 GB UFS外置: microSD (class 10, 最大2 TB)<br />\n顯示器\t5.7 吋 IGZO LCD 1440&times;2560120 Hz 廣色域 (WCG)<br />\nCorning Gorilla Glass 3<br />\n主鏡頭\t12MP AF f1.75 廣角12MP AF f2.6 縮放<br />\n雙 PDAF<br />\n雙色調雙 LED 閃光燈<br />\n前置鏡頭\t8 MP FF f2.0<br />\n音效\t立體聲前方喇叭<br />\n雙重放大器<br />\nTHX 認證 DAC 音效介面<br />\n電源\t4,000mAh 鋰離子電池Qualcomm&reg; Quick Charge&trade; 4+<br />\n無線\t802.11 a/b/g/n/ac藍牙 4.2<br />\nNFC<br />\n頻道\t四頻道 GSM UMTS：B1/2/3/4/5/8LTE:B1/2/3/4/5/7/8/12/17/19/20/25/26/28/29/30/66<br />\nTDD LTE: B38/39/40/41 TD-SCDMA: B34/39<br />\n尺寸\t158.5 x 77.7 x 8 毫米6.24 x 3.06 x 0.31 吋<br />\n197 克<br />\nAndroid 版本\tNougat 7.1.1<br />\n<br />\n此文章原刊於 <a href=\"http://Qooah.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FQooah.com&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=a612edcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Qooah.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/razer-phone-%E9%9B%B7%E8%9B%87%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%90%88%E7%90%86-062057532.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkstylemen.yahoo.com%2Frazer-phone-%25E9%259B%25B7%25E8%259B%2587%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E4%25BD%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%2590%2586-062057532.html&d=DgJ1U%2FQ4SkTgvWt%2FEKlm%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=10a925b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkstylemen.yahoo.com/razer-phone-%E9%9B%B7%E8%9B%87%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E5%90%88%E7%90%86-062057532.html</a>"},{"pid":"5b1b91082351ca62361b6626a4af9a2aa26a79d8","tid":493484,"uid":29625,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"Razer QC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n部嘢一年內唔壞當你贏"},{"pid":"a21cc462e17177452266740d48fdb79ff271fa09","tid":493484,"uid":65144,"like":32,"dislike":16,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"6000蚊買android 機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 憑咩收大廠旗艦機價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重有買電子產品唔好買第一代係常識"},{"pid":"c258d3bf164308bd7a740454aeeae538c7a95df7","tid":493484,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:09:43.000Z","msg":"白老鼠機on99"},{"pid":"0ffa688bf324c84352176b113431b997406d3e53","tid":493484,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"Razer<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43cf552d4cddd0d214672eb9b4f71656ead5db1","tid":4934